### Complete API Test Suite
### Sử dụng với REST Client extension trong VS Code

### ==================== ROLE MANAGEMENT ====================

### 1. Tạo Role
POST http://localhost:3000/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleName": "Student",
  "description": "Học viên trong hệ thống"
}

### 2. Lấy danh sách Roles
GET http://localhost:3000/roles

### 3. Lấy chi tiết Role
GET http://localhost:3000/roles/1

### 4. Lấy thống kê Role
GET http://localhost:3000/roles/1/stats

### ==================== EXAM MANAGEMENT ====================

### 5. Tạo Exam
POST http://localhost:3000/exams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "English Grammar Test - Level 1",
  "description": "Bài kiểm tra ngữ pháp tiếng Anh cơ bản",
  "duration": 60,
  "difficulty": "Easy",
  "isActive": true
}

### 6. Lấy danh sách Exams
GET http://localhost:3000/exams

### 7. Lấy Exams theo difficulty
GET http://localhost:3000/exams?difficulty=Easy

### 8. Lấy Active Exams
GET http://localhost:3000/exams/active

### 9. Lấy chi tiết Exam
GET http://localhost:3000/exams/1

### 10. Lấy thống kê Exam
GET http://localhost:3000/exams/1/stats

